Package com.empirilytics.qatch.core.eval

Class IssueSet

java.lang.Object
com.empirilytics.qatch.core.eval.IssueSet
public class IssueSet extends Object
A class that represents a set of violations of a certain file (i.e. class) or a whole project in general.

For the benchmarking we do not pay attention to each class separately, but to the total number of the violations for the whole project.

Typically it is a vector of issues. An IssueSet holds all the violations (i.e. issues) of a certain Property (i.e Rule Set) of the total Project.
